258
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:33,464
but that's not it at all.

259
00:20:33,559 --> 00:20:35,776
You're constantly

260
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:38,776
thinking about someone.

261
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:43,135
