268
00:21:00,559 --> 00:21:02,995
Please, I beg you, help me.

269
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:05,120
For the past six months,

270
00:21:05,839 --> 00:21:07,019
I've only been sleeping two

271
00:21:07,035 --> 00:21:08,198
or three hours a day.

272
00:21:09,519 --> 00:21:10,640
Alright.

273
00:21:11,279 --> 00:21:13,135
I'll give you a method.

274
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:15,393
Whether it cures your heartache or not

275
00:21:15,519 --> 00:21:17,885
depends on your own fate.

276
00:21:18,279 --> 00:21:20,885
Thank you, Grandma Yu. Please, tell me.

277
00:21:21,799 --> 00:21:23,079
Child,

278
00:21:23,319 --> 00:21:27,034
you've endured too much pain.

279
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:31,143
If you truly wish to forget them,

280
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,503
you must not only

281
00:21:32,528 --> 00:21:34,261
continue thinking of them,

282
00:21:34,345 --> 00:21:36,113
but also revisit the places where

283
00:21:36,137 --> 00:21:37,870
you once loved each other,

284
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:40,565
eat the food you once shared,

285
00:21:40,672 --> 00:21:42,117
and walk the paths

286
00:21:42,142 --> 00:21:43,822
you once walked together.

287
00:21:44,343 --> 00:21:48,362
You must confront all those memories

288
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:52,079
the mundane, the joyful, the painful.

289
00:21:52,359 --> 00:21:53,718
In the end, the answer

290
00:21:53,743 --> 00:21:55,289
